short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Speed Dial changes the standard page to the new tab page with your saved bookmarks

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This free add-on for Chrome Browser allows you navigate to your custom bookmarks quickly and easily. Set a background from an image gallery powered by Unsplash in your Chrome Browser default new tab. We are actually changing your Chrome browser default new tab page. Also as added features; create bookmarks groups, place bookmarks into the groups, set the number of bookmarks shown, reset settings, and search for information, images, video, and more through Bing search. There is also a Digital Clock in new tabs where you can check your time in 12 or 24-hour format.
